column3: style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 1.5em; padding: 0px;">If you want to achieve that warm and cosy ambience in your bach or home, the 3D Beige Wallpaper is something that you should take a squiz at.It is a waterproof and lightweight vinyl un-prepasted wallpaper designed to impress your family and visitors and make them feel at home. With its superior standard quality, this can surely last on your walls for a long time. Whether you want to use it in your restaurant, office, living room, bedroom, study area, kid’s play area, etc., this wallpaper will instantly set the mood of your space and showcase your creative side. Meanwhile, its subtle beige colour will make a great pair to any of your furniture and decorations at home. Plus, it’s designed to be fairly quick and easy to install, so you can  do it yourself without a hassle.  The 3D Beige Wallpaper set comes with one (1) glue and one (1) primer.
